The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

", "id": "ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Opening Hours.

Our normal opening hours are open from 11:00 a.m to 11:00 p.m. with a licence that extends until 12:00 and later for special occasion such as on New Year's Eve for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball.

With room for up to 200 people, The Horns pub is an excellent place for parties and celebrations.

", "id": "74d3609c-28c1-4f89-9286-0bd3834c5087"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

Bands and Gigs At the Horns.

", "id": "703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

The Horns Pub is known and loved for live music and for featuring some of the best bands and artist from near and far.

We have regular gigs and music nights and music to suit many tastes.

The Horns gigs feature some well known and popular bands along with tribute bands other performances by popular artists.

WHITLEY NEILL GINS.

", "id": "be11fb91-7c23-4965-af18-f614f7464171"}]}, "id": "9fe8d5b0-d95b-4767-b960-740bdd410f78"}]}, "id": "4f1c85b5-8e43-4706-b3ad-7d4f0e1bafaa"}]}, "id": "5bdce5e7-12fd-418c-b121-9c9b9e84c96f"}, {"type": "row", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "", "custom_id": ""}, "fluid": false, "content": [{"type": "content", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "my-3 text-center", "custom_id": "", "column_breakpoint": "md"}, "column_size": "", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "

About Gin.

", "id": "cb145ff3-3fcc-4e27-bb3f-29b77ab8d3f0"}]}, "id": "c4fb35a8-76b9-45b7-b8fc-a5b9e0f1d699"}]}, "id": "6ec04129-ba61-4d2e-9108-091180eba388"}, {"type": "row", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "", "custom_id": ""}, "fluid": false, "content": [{"type": "content", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "bounce_element align-middle", "custom_id": "", "column_breakpoint": "md"}, "column_size": "", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

Usually, Gin is mixed with Tonic water which is made with quinine to add some bitter favour, which is also often mixed with other fruity or herbal flavours.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\u00e9vrier.

", "id": "7f38d4de-e7db-4f1d-9e0e-b5715442a04d"}]}, "id": "4c5781f4-636a-43b2-82a7-bf7c35966b6e"}]}, "id": "29b46053-86ed-4e5d-8652-32ce399ff57b"}, {"type": "row", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "bg-light", "custom_id": ""}, "fluid": true, "content": [{"type": "content", "value": {"settings": {"custom_template": "", "custom_css_class": "text-center my-2", "custom_id": "", "column_breakpoint": "md"}, "column_size": "", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "

WHITLEY NEILL BLACKBERRY GIN
Fresh plump berries and hints of floral hedgerow are finished with warming cassia spice.
Paired with Fever Tree Elderflower tonic garnished with fresh blackberries.

", "id": "02a3400b-c4fb-4e8f-a572-8d72dbb0ec13"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

WHITLEY NEILL BLOOD ORANGE GIN
A refreshing, intense orange aroma, with hints of liquorice and coriander.
Paired with Fever Tree Mediterranean tonic garnished with orange.

", "id": "2050d6af-13b2-4cf5-a25c-1d2155d82f3d"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

WHITLEY NEILL PARMA VIOLET GIN
Bright vibrant flavours of juniper followed by a herbaceous floral note from the Violet.
Paired with Fever Tree Elderflower tonic garnished with strawberry.

", "id": "3cc774b1-f5d2-462f-8b5a-dc5096f0cc50"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

WHITLEY NEILL PINK GRAPEFRUIT GIN
A delicate sweetness with citrusy notes that give way to a balanced grapefruit burst.
Paired with Fever Tree Mediterranean tonic, garnished with a slice of pink grapefruit.

", "id": "ab8a8858-2e9a-498b-a246-8ea612ba962f"}, {"type": "text", "value": "

WHITLEY NEILL RHUBARB & GINGER GIN
Subtly tart with clear rhubarb influence. A twist of orange sweetness and herbaceous coriander brings balance to the palate.
Paired with Fever Tree Indian tonic, garnished with orange.

GORDONS PINK GIN

The natural sweetness of raspberries and strawberries balance with the tang of redcurrant, served up in a unique blushing tone.

Paired with Fever Tree lemon tonic garnished with mint.

GORDON\u2019S LONDON DRY GIN

A traditional refreshing taste from the finest handpicked juniper berries and a selection of other botanicals. Served with Fever Tree refreshingly light tonic garnished with a lemon wheel.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

On New Year's Eve, we also have extended hours for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

On New Year's Eve, we also have extended hours for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

Usually, Gin is mixed with Tonic water which is made with quinine to add some bitter favour, which is also often mixed with other fruity or herbal flavours.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\\u00e9vrier.

\", \"id\": \"5f3157fc-4140-49b1-931d-e6f4abfe6548\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

Usually, Gin is mixed with Tonic water which is made with quinine to add some bitter favour, which is also often mixed with other fruity or herbal flavours.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\\u00e9vrier.

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\\u00e9vrier.

A traditional refreshing taste from the finest handpicked juniper berries and a selection of other botanicals. Served with Fever Tree refreshingly light tonic garnished with a lemon wheel.

The natural sweetness of raspberries and strawberries balance with the tang of redcurrant, served up in a unique blushing tone.

paired with fever Tree Indian tonic garnished with a lime wedge.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

Usually, Gin is mixed with Tonic water which is made with quinine to add some bitter favour, which is also often mixed with other fruity or herbal flavours.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\\u00e9vrier.

Gin is a refreshing alcoholic drink made from juniper berries which give it its distinctive taste. Gin is often mixed with any combination of herbal, spice, floral or fruit flavours to produce a fresh and exciting beverage.

Usually, Gin is mixed with Tonic water which is made with quinine to add some bitter favour, which is also often mixed with other fruity or herbal flavours.

The name Gin is taken from French for Juniper Gen\\u00e9vrier.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Our normal opening hours are open from 11:00 a.m to 11:00 p.m. with a licence that extends until 12:00 or 1.00 a.m. on music evenings.

On New Year's Eve, we also have extended hours for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball.

We also have extended hours for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball on New Year's Eve.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Our normal opening hours are open from 11:00 a.m to 11:00 p.m. with a licence that extends until 12:00 or 1.00 a.m. on music evenings.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Bar in Watford

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

\", \"id\": \"703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Bands and Gigs At the Horns.

\", \"id\": \"703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

The Horns Pub is known and loved for live music and for featuring some of the best bands and artist from near and far.

We have regular gigs and music nights and music to suit many tastes.

The Horns gigs feature some well known and popular bands along with tribute bands other performances by popular artists.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Bands and Gigs At the Horns.

\", \"id\": \"703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

The Horns Pub is known and loved for live music and for featuring some of the best bands and artist from near and far.

We have regular gigs and music nights and music to suit many tastes.

The Horns gigs feature some well known and popular bands along with tribute bands other performances by popular artists.

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

The Best Live Music Bar in Watford.

\", \"id\": \"ca0034e4-282a-4f6a-b894-01e50747cf8c\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

We are the best live music venue in Watford and have been bringing live music to you since 2001, while remaining a traditional pub. We welcome all ages until 8pm daily, after which time it is over-18\\u2019s only. We have a large air-conditioned open bar with capacity for over 250 people and enclosed beer garden with lighting and heating. Whether you are coming for lunch, looking for a great evening of live music, just popping in for a drink or looking for a good pint of real ale (all our pumps carry the Cask Marque) we are the place for you, and our very friendly & accommodating staff will do all they can to help.

Opening Hours.

Our normal opening hours are open from 11:00 a.m to 11:00 p.m. with a licence that extends until 12:00 and later for special occasion such as on New Year's Eve for our famed New Year's Eve celebration ball.

With room for up to 200 people, The Horns pub is an excellent place for parties and celebrations.

\", \"id\": \"703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f\"}]}, \"id\": \"4ea53c69-5e08-4bc0-aa5f-263328795e1b\"}]}, \"id\": \"b2e0d0b2-9082-4cf7-85f7-9c9d1ccbfdfa\"}]}, \"id\": \"7ae9cdfb-bbe7-4732-9148-7bff4442d68d\"}, {\"type\": \"hero\", \"value\": {\"settings\": {\"custom_template\": \"\", \"custom_css_class\": \"bg-light text-dark bg_img_with_opacity d-block my-auto\", \"custom_id\": \"Whats On Section\"}, \"fluid\": true, \"is_parallax\": false, \"background_image\": null, \"tile_image\": false, \"background_color\": \"\", \"foreground_color\": \"\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"row\", \"value\": {\"settings\": {\"custom_template\": \"\", \"custom_css_class\": \"\", \"custom_id\": \"\"}, \"fluid\": false, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"content\", \"value\": {\"settings\": {\"custom_template\": \"\", \"custom_css_class\": \"d-block my-auto\", \"custom_id\": \"\", \"column_breakpoint\": \"md\"}, \"column_size\": \"6\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

What's on at the Horns Pub.

\", \"id\": \"74d3609c-28c1-4f89-9286-0bd3834c5087\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

Bands and Gigs At the Horns.

\", \"id\": \"703f8367-a6c2-42de-a6a8-067b7534321f\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"value\": \"

The Horns Pub is known and loved for live music and for featuring some of the best bands and artist from near and far.

We have regular gigs and music nights and music to suit many tastes.

The Horns gigs feature some well known and popular bands along with tribute bands other performances by popular artists.
